  "body": "This is a suggestion, but I don't see the advantage of not compiling the contracts, and it makes `truffle exec` less useful if you have to compile them manually before each run. \r\n\r\nI always end up doing: \r\n```\r\nnpx truffle compile && npx truffle exec myScript.js\r\n```",
