    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks @maraoz, this seems right. \r\n\r\nAfter some discussion with @gnidan, have implemented this as an option in [truffle-core 132](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-core/pull/132) e.g:\r\n```\r\ntruffle exec [-c | --compile] <script.js>\r\n```\r\n`compile` overwrites the artifact bytecode so it might be safest to require the user express a clear intent here - it's a change in default behavior that saves to file. \r\n\r\nShould be in the next patch release, thanks again. ",
